- **Project model**
  - `id`: String @id @default(cuid())
  - `title`: String
  - `theme`: String?  (optional board theme)
  - `columns`: Relation to [Column](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) model
  - `members`: Many-to-many relation via [BoardMember](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `groups`: Many-to-many relation for sharing with [Group](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `createdAt`, `updatedAt`: timestamp fields

- **Column model**
  - `id`, `title`, `width`: basic column metadata
  - `projectId`: foreign key to [Project](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `cards`: Relation to [Card](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) model
  - `createdAt`, `updatedAt`: timestamp fields

- **Card model**
  - `id`, `title`, `description`: core card fields
  - `labels`: Many-to-many with [Label](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `dueDate`: DateTime? for optional due date
  - `assignees`: Many-to-many relation with [User](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) model
  - `priority`: uses [Priority enum](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `attachments`: One-to-many with [Attachment](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `comments`: One-to-many with [Comment](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `milestone`: Optional relation to [Milestone](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) model
  - `columnId`: foreign key to [Column](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `order`: Float (supports decimal ordering)
  - `createdAt`, `updatedAt`: timestamp fields

- **Label model**
  - `id`, `name`, `color`
  - `cards`: Many-to-many back to [Card](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)

- **Attachment model**
  - `id`, `name`, `url`, `type`
  - `cardId`: foreign key to [Card](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `createdAt`: timestamp

- **Comment model**
  - `id`, `authorId`: foreign key to [User](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `content`: String
  - `cardId`: foreign key to [Card](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `createdAt`: timestamp

- **Priority enum**
  - Defines card priority levels: `low`, `medium`, `high`

- **User model**
  - `id`, `name`, `email`, `image`: standard user fields (likely from NextAuth)
  - `boards`: Many-to-many relation via [BoardMember](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `assignedCards`: Many-to-many relation back to [Card](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `comments`: One-to-many relation back to [Comment](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `groups`: Many-to-many relation via [GroupMember](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)

- **BoardMember model** (Join table for Project <-> User)
  - `projectId`: foreign key to [Project](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `userId`: foreign key to [User](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `role`: Enum (e.g., `ADMIN`, `MEMBER`, `VIEWER`)
  - Assigned `createdAt`, `updatedAt`

- **Milestone model**
  - `id`, `title`, `description`, `dueDate`
  - `projectId`: foreign key to [Project](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) (milestones belong to a project)
  - `cards`: One-to-many relation back to [Card](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)

- **Group model**
  - `id`, `name`: basic group info
  - `members`: Many-to-many relation via [GroupMember](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `boards`: Many-to-many relation for shared [Project](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)s

- **GroupMember model** (Join table for Group <-> User)
  - `groupId`: foreign key to [Group](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - `userId`: foreign key to [User](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma)
  - Assigned `createdAt`
